OL,3,CSanex shower gel advert banned over
OL,4,C'offensive racial stereotype'
OL,6,FA TV advert for Sanex shower gel has
OL,7,Fbeen banned over an "offensive racial
OL,8,Fstereotype", the advertising watchdog
OL,9,Fhas said.
OL,11,FThe advert, which aired in June,
OL,12,Fshowed a black woman with red scratch
OL,13,Fmarks and covered in clay-like
OL,14,Fmaterial before cutting to a scene of
OL,15,Fa white woman showering.
OL,17,FThe Advertising Standards Authority
OL,18,F(ASA) has ruled the advert must not
OL,19,Fappear again, finding viewers could
OL,20,Finterpret it as suggesting that "white
OL,21,Fskin was superior to black skin".
