OL,6,FThe watchdog received two complaints
OL,7,Fabout the content.
OL,9,F"The ad was therefore structured in
OL,10,Fsuch a way that it was the black skin,
OL,11,Fdepicted in association with itchy and
OL,12,Fdry skin, which was shown to be
OL,13,Fproblematic and uncomfortable, whereas
OL,14,Fthe white skin, depicted as smoother
OL,15,Fand clean after using the product, was
OL,16,Fshown successfully changed and
OL,17,Fresolved," the watchdog said.
