OL,6,F"Although we understood that this
OL,7,Fmessage was not the one intended and
OL,8,Fmight appear coincidental or pass
OL,9,Funnoticed by some viewers, we
OL,10,Fconsidered that the ad was likely to
OL,11,Freinforce the negative and offensive
OL,12,Fracial stereotype that black skin was
OL,13,Fproblematic and that white skin was
OL,14,Fsuperior.
OL,16,F"We concluded that the ad included a
OL,17,Fracial stereotype and was therefore
OL,18,Flikely to cause serious offence."
