OL,11,FColgate-Palmolive, which owns the
OL,12,FSanex brand, said it did not believe
OL,13,Fthe advert perpetuated negative racial
OL,14,Fstereotypes nor was it likely to cause
OL,15,Fserious offence.
OL,17,FIt said the depiction of diverse
OL,18,Fmodels in the advert was designed to
OL,19,Fshow the product was suitable and
OL,20,Feffective for all and was not a
OL,21,Fcomparison based on race or ethnicity.
